  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK510">
<l>tērāṉ ṟeḷivun teḷintāṉka ṇaiyuṟavun </l>
<l> tīrā viṭumpai tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To make choice of one who has not been examined, and to entertain doubts respecting one who has been chosen, will produce irremediable sorrow.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
